{"tid":1598661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗天主教中學副校長陳秀芳投訴電郵 比大家參考","createTime":"2019-09-27T14:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T17:34:14.000Z","uid":292771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"24d3b7c97b8fc8adcb53eac860cc76044ff4e1f0","tid":1598661,"uid":292771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"你好:<br />\n有關日前網上流傳一則元朗天主教中學副校長陳秀芳出言不遜，有違師表。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CnEEGUilv88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCnEEGUilv88&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=05e4bb83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CnEEGUilv88</a><br />\n有鑑於早前2013年8月4日中午在香港旺角西洋菜街行人專用區講粗口實為同一事件，但不見最近教育局有任何形式或相同於林老師一樣的刑責。<br />\n是否有違雙重標準，請儘早處理，以免教育局聲譽有損。<br />\n<br />\n名自肯決定<br />\n香港市民上<br />\nfeedback@hkptu.org<br />\nhkcsco@catholic.org.hk<br />\nedbcomp@edb.gov.hk"},{"pid":"13c3981899e620a90beb7d9ac389bbce144beb02","tid":1598661,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aca94534b458191bb457e25733c4757292a1f94","tid":1598661,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"「推上熱門」 9.28 行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1598677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1598677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"970435123f0475d61077d864f4ac9c0c55c205af","tid":1598661,"uid":292771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc2ebaaa6902882e311d377594b44a9e69400296","tid":1598661,"uid":193786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:34:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}